╛The IATP - Raising Asbestos Awareness Together
Remembering those whose lives have been affected by asbestos
The living owe it to those who can no longer speak
to tell their story for them"─
┴Here is where good friends should meet
To laugh and talk on Sammy's seat
In loving memory of
Samantha Jane Thompson 1981 - 2009
She brought laughter into our lives
and love into our hearts"┘
╓In loving memory of Peter Newens
1922-2010
My darling Peter I know that you are near
for still I hold your unseen hand your silent voice I hear.
Love forever Jane

Jane Newens
1921-2020
"Together Once More""▄
